AVISION INC (2380)  said unconsolidated sales
in April rose 30.90% to NT$262,611,000 from NT$200,622,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales            262,611          200,622    
YOY%              30.90%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            858,869          988,512    
YOY%             -13.11% 
=================================================================
 